OL,3,CNew accommodation for those travelling
OL,4,Cfrom Isles of Scilly for treatment
OL,6,FIsles of Scilly residents who need to
OL,7,Ftravel to the mainland for medical
OL,8,Ftreatment will be able to stay in new
OL,9,Faccommodation near Treliske Hospital.
OL,11,FCharity has bought a five-bedroom
OL,12,Fproperty, just a few minutes walk from
OL,13,Fthe hospital which is the nearest
OL,14,Fmajor treatment site for islanders.
