OL,3,CNew accommodation for those travelling
OL,4,Cfrom Isles of Scilly for treatment
OL,6,FThe property will provide a space for
OL,7,Fislanders undergoing longer-term
OL,8,Foutpatient treatment, for loved ones
OL,9,Faccompanying patients during emergency
OL,10,Ftreatment, and for patients discharged
OL,11,Fat times when travel home to the
OL,12,Fislands is impossible.
OL,14,FThe Island Haven is run entirely by
OL,15,Fvolunteers and has been fundraising
OL,16,Ffor the site since 2019. It hopes to
OL,17,Fhave the facility available by the end
OL,18,Fof 2024.
