OL,3,CNew accommodation for those travelling
OL,4,Cfrom Isles of Scilly for treatment
OL,6,FCurrently islanders have to pay for
OL,7,Faccommodation when travelling to
OL,8,FCornwall for treatment, which can be
OL,9,Fmade more difficult by tourism in the
OL,10,Fsummer months.
OL,12,FThe plans are for four affordable
OL,13,Fensuite double bedrooms, a communal
OL,14,Fkitchen and shared social space, as
OL,15,Fwell as a small garden and car parking.
