OL,6,F"However, this pivot in our plans
OL,7,Fmeans The Island Haven is now truly on
OL,8,Fits feet, with a very real prospect
OL,9,Fthat this vital facility will be
OL,10,Favailable for those who need it before
OL,11,Fthe end of this year.
OL,13,F"We really cannot emphasise enough our
OL,14,Fgratitude to the small but dedicated
OL,15,Fcommunity of Scilly ` islanders,
OL,16,Fvisitors and businesses ` who have
OL,17,Fmade this a reality.
