OL,6,F"We also wish to sincerely thank
OL,7,Fsolicitors Alison Morden-Hawke and
OL,8,FNikki Jonas of Womble, Bond, Dickinson
OL,9,F(UK) LLP and property surveyor Brian
OL,10,FHasell of Huntley & Partners for their
OL,11,Fprofessional services, enabling the
OL,12,Fpurchase to proceed."
OL,14,FThe charity will now continue to
OL,15,Ffundraise to convert, update and equip
OL,16,Fthe property and fund the ongoing
OL,17,Frunning and maintenance costs.
OL,19,FIt's currently working alongside the
OL,20,FRoyal Cornwall Hospitals Trust to
OL,21,Fprovide on-campus accommodation.
